---
---

<section class="insight" aria-label="User testimonial">
  <div class="insight__inner">
    <blockquote class="insight__quote">
      "I've tried many fasting apps, but most felt overwhelming. They made fasting feel like a huge commitment. If I missed a few days, I felt like I failed.<br />This app feels different. It feels intentional. I love how simple it is. The &#x201C;Freeze Streak&#x201D; feature is a great idea."
    </blockquote>
    <img
      src="/monia.png"
      class="insight__avatar"
      alt="Monika"
      width="48"
      height="48"
    />
    <p class="insight__name">Monika, 34</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .insight {
    padding: 52px 0;
  }

  .insight__inner {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .insight__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-align: center;
    color: #0A0A0A;
  }

  .insight__avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .insight__name {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-align: center;
    color: #0A0A0A;
  }
</style>
